# `nix build` drops a `result` symlink into the flake dir. It points into
# /nix/store/... INSIDE the build box — a path that does not exist on the host
# (the whole point of this lab is that the host has no Nix). Committing it leaves
# a dangling symlink in the repo, which is exactly what happened in 7d8b5f7.
result
result-*
